      const type = form.dataset.disabilityEligibilityType;
      form.addEventListener("submit", (event2) => {

          token

        buttonParent.appendChild(loadingIndicator);
        yr.ajax({
          type: "POST",
          url: "/services/disability_eligibility.php",
          dataType: "json",
          data: dataToSend,
          success: (data) => {
            if (data.status === "success") {
